title: MongoDB with PHP Build OOP Website Prepare for the future
description:
Description

Learn working with Mongo, Compass and PHP by building an OOP website together.Also learn more about Ajax calls, Pagination, Creating a Cart System from scratch, OOP, Login and Register System.Add an interesting website to your portfolio and learn how to insert and retrieve pictures directly in MongoDB, Find, Cursor, Projection, Push…and much
Who is the target audience?

    PHP learners

Requirements

    Basic PHP/SQL programming
